import React from 'react';
import {Nav,NavLink,Bars,NavMenu,NavBtn,NavBtnLink,} from './NavBarElements';


const Navbar = () => {
    return (
      <>
        <Nav>
          <Bars />
          <NavMenu>
            <NavLink to='/' activeStyle={{color:'red'}} exact>
              Home
            </NavLink>
            <NavLink to='/ingredients' activeStyle={{color:'red'}}>
              Ingredients
            </NavLink>
            <NavLink to='/products' activeStyle={{color:'red'}}>
              Products
            </NavLink>
            <NavLink to='/recipes' activeStyle={{color:'red'}}>
              Recipes
            </NavLink>
            <NavLink to='/register' activeStyle={{color:'red'}}>
              Register
            </NavLink>
            <NavLink to='/login' activeStyle={{color:'red'}}>
              Login
            </NavLink>

          </NavMenu>

        </Nav>
      </>
    );
  };
    
  export default Navbar;
